The paper addresses the problem of video representation learning, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed approach is self-supervised, which is also a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The approach focuses on spatio-temporal features, which are important in multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) tasks.
